- AND MY FEELING IS THAT
EVERGLADES NATIONAL PARK

00:25:12.700 --> 00:25:15.460
PROVIDES A VERY
UNIQUE OPPORTUNITY

00:25:15.460 --> 00:25:18.530
TO THE RESIDENTS
