MILE UPON MILE
OF INTACT WETLANDS,

00:25:34.830 --> 00:25:38.500
A LOW COUNTRY WHERE ONLY AN
INCH OF RISE IN ELEVATION

00:25:38.500 --> 00:25:41.460
CAN SPELL THE DIFFERENCE
BETWEEN GRASSY PRAIRIE

00:25:41.460 --> 00:25:43.230
AND WOODED HAMMOCK.

