CORAL REEFS ARE THE MOST
BIOLOGICALLY DIVERSE

00:29:29.330 --> 00:29:31.260
COMMUNITIES IN THE
MARINE ENVIRONMENT

00:29:31.260 --> 00:29:33.230
AROUND THE WORLD.

00:29:33.230 --> 00:29:36.630
THE NATURAL BEAUTY HERE,
AS ABUNDANT ABOVE WATER

00:29:36.630 --> 00:29:40.830
AS BELOW, ATTRACTS
THOUSANDS OF TOURISTS.

