AND SOME, FALLING IN LOVE
WITH WILD BEACHES LIKE

00:29:44.760 --> 00:29:48.630
BAHIA HONDA STATE PARK,
MAKE THE KEYS THEIR HOME.

00:29:48.630 --> 00:29:51.060
THOSE ARE SOME OF MY
ABSOLUTE FAVORITE PLACES

00:29:51.060 --> 00:29:52.200
IN THE KEYS.

00:29:52.200 --> 00:29:54.600
AND I LOVE BEACHES
AND I LOVE ANYWHERE

00:29:54.600 --> 00:29:57.860
WHERE THE OCEAN AND THE
LAND COMES TOGETHER.

00:29:57.860 --> 00:30:02.460
AND THAT BEACH TENDS TO BE
KIND OF WILD AND WINDSWEPT.

