CORAL BLEACHING, WHILE
A NATURAL PART OF A

00:30:50.860 --> 00:30:53.800
SYMBIOTIC RELATIONSHIP
SUPPORTING CORAL GROWTH

00:30:53.800 --> 00:30:56.860
AND ALGAE, NOW APPEARS
AT UNPRECEDENTED LEVELS

00:30:56.860 --> 00:30:59.230
AROUND THE WORLD.

