MASSIVE CORAL BLEACHING
EVENTS WERE FIRST OBSERVED

00:31:02.060 --> 00:31:03.530
IN THE MID 70'S,

00:31:03.530 --> 00:31:05.900
AND THEY HAVE PICKED UP
IN FREQUENCY SINCE THEN

00:31:05.900 --> 00:31:08.630
EVOLVING FROM
ISOLATED LOCAL EVENTS

00:31:08.630 --> 00:31:11.900
TO REGIONAL TO
GLOBAL IN SCALE.

